column11: Chronic pain? Soreness or knots in the hip, shoulders, lower back? Headache? or just stress from work... all is treated here at Meridian Massage &Cupping, we offer full body massage.let your pain and tension melt away.Working with acupuncture points, we can help you access deep healing by offering Basic Craniosacral Massage, Lymphatic Drainage Massage, and foot/hands/ears reflexology, Shiatsu, Deep Tissue Massage , Cupping, Guasha.We activate the 14 energy meridians on the human body with light touches on acupuncture points -- similar to Swedish massage and Hot Stone .We offer deep pressure by following Meridian to for the Glutes, Quads, and Entire Leg Region. Pectoralis major, Deltoid, Rhomboid minor and major, Latissimus Doris .Sports therapy.Many clients report feeling lighter upon waking, warmer lower back, and smoother digestive system for days and weeks after massage.My goal is to bring you to a deeply relaxed state with my decade-long experience in therapeutic massage.Expertise in:Shiatsu Acupuncture PointsDeep Tissue Cupping Hot StoneSwedish Reflexology Specialty Certified: Guasha, MoxibustionMeridian Massage & Cupping(141 N Martinwood Rd suite 104-10)M-F 10:00AM - 7:00PMSat 11:00 AM - 6:00PMPhone:  show contact infoPlease call to make an appointmentAddress:141 N Martinwood Rd suite 104 Rm 10 knoxville TN 37923Located: behind Grayson Hyundai & Subaru (Exit 379 Bridgewater Rd to Kingston Pike turn right to go 2 blocks to Martinwood Rd, turn right onto the last building (Building Name: The Avenue)

column11: Uptight? Overworked? Job stress?Escape from the world for a while!The massage you will receive is not the usual programmed bodywork you may have gotten in the past. I can begin to relieve your muscular discomfort from weekend warrior activities, weightlifting, working long hours at the computer, or just simply need relaxation. My massages are intuitive, focusing on areas that need attention. Upper back pain and discomfort are addressed, carpal tunnel, shoulders, glutes, inner and outer thighs and abs are all worked. I do some stretches during the massage, to aid the muscles to lengthen and get the soreness out. My training is in modalities that can relieve your discomfort and let your muscles "let go" and relax. Heated table, warm oils, shower available$60.00 per hr. $80.00 per 1  hours.Heated table, warm oils, Quiet country setting. column11: Hello!My name is Rue. I am a Massage Therapist in Asheville, North Carolina. My approach to massage resets the nervous system, coaxes the muscles to release tension, and mobilizes the joints so you can move about life a little easier. If you are experiencing discomfort or stress in your body from labor or life, massage can help. I want to work with you on the specific needs of your body, and customize the massage to fit you.My rates are:60 minutes = $60This session is the perfect break in your day, ideal for stress release and relaxation. column11: My name is Kelly and I am a Body Works practitioner. I offer body rubs; am experienced in Energy Transfer, Shiatsu Stretching, Ashiatsu, Swedish, Deep Tissue, Lomi-Lomi, Esalen body rubs & now offer faciaIs.  I operate out of a studio in my Weaverville townhome- a quiet and safe neighborhood. Please keep in mind that I usually need 24 hrs notice, or at least the night before you'd like to come in(by 9:30pm). Due to the high volume of calls, I won't be taking more than 2-3 appointments max in a day. My business hours are: 11am-8pm, Mon-Fri. Occasional exceptions are made for an earlier or later time. - Private studio for one on one body Tx.  - Heated and wide massage table with memory foam face cradle.  - Guest bathroom w/shower available; towels and neutral hygiene products. - Aromatherapy.  - Enjoyable background music.  - Each session is catered to the individual.  - Finger, toenail clippings and general grooming. - Body scrubs available and reasonably priced. - FaciaI sessions.  I am a STRICTLY PLATONIC PRACTITIONER. I do "body rubs" as I am unlicensed in NC at this time. I do require minimal draping-- but I require that clients maintain the utmost of respect at all times. I do NONSENSUAL sessions so please Do Not Ask. Body Sessions: $80/60min, $110/90min, $140/120min.  NEW CLIENT PRICES: $60/60min, $90/90min, $120/120min. FaciaIs: $40/each Text, call, email, or make request via website(text preferred) to make appointment. I can't always answer emails and calls right away-- but I'll be checking them daily and texts as often during the day as I can. column11: Hello! I am pleased to offer my gifts of warmth and unconditional love to people who would be served by an hour-long platonic cuddle session. What do I mean by "Platonic"?This is non-sexual. We will be fully clothed. My energy feels like that of a loving mother, a soothing therapist, a reassuring friend. What do I mean by "Cuddle"?We sit/recline on a couch, with my arm around you//your arm around me. Breathing deeply together. Perhaps talking, perhaps not. Gentle, soothing touch. Perhaps some light massage to help you relax, or to help us connect. Many people are served by the joy of being held close in a loving, platonic embrace. It eases people into feeling comfortable with touch if they are recovering from trauma, or are unfamiliar with touch. Being held helps people to feel safe crying, releasing emotions, laughing, and feeling worthy and deserving of love, in its purest form. "Being held by Hannah helped me relax and feel what was going on in my heart." Why me?I am a mother, an experienced joy coach, and pretty much everyone I'm close with tells me that they are unusually comfortable with me. People love to open up to me, share pieces of themselves that have been hidden. I have a comfy body, and find it very natural to get snuggly with people. I have noticed that when I offer to snuggle people, they have told me that it is rare for them, and very healing, to get to be held in the way that I hold.How it works:You respond in an e-mail with: why you would be served by platonic cuddling, your name, your phone number, and a good time to call you. From there, we will discuss our intentions on the phone, and if we're on the same page, set up a time to meet. The cost?The cost for a one-hour session, including a 5-15 minute intro conversation, is $100. I require a $25 initial payment after our phone call to reserve my time. The rest can be paid at the completion of the session.

My routine usually leaves people in a deeply inner-connected, trance like state; so, they are very happy they are at home and can enjoy remaining in that state instead of having to come out of it to drive home.Most people say they sleep deeper, are more calm, and mentally focused for about a week after the massage. column11: Over 25 years of experience  Graduate of the Swedish Institute of New York, 1986. Board Certified and licensed  Doctor's Degree from Logan College of Chiropractic, St Louis Missouri, 1994. Previous clients include Elizabeth Taylor, Paloma Picasso and Aida Turturro  LGBT friendly  My work is the perfect combination of Deep/therapeutic and soothing/Swedish massage. I can work out the problem areas and/or give you an incredibly relaxing treatment.  I'm particularly skilled at working out issues in the back, shoulders and neck. My glute, chest, belly and foot massage is even more amazing.  Together, we'll figure out the perfect massage to fit your specific needs. Available for singles, couples, groups and parties. Your place or mine.  Massages are available from 20 minutes to 3 hours or more. Prices start at $60 an hour for soothing/therapeutic. Deep tissue massage is also available for $40 per half hour or $80 for an hour.  There is an additional charge for outcalls, depending on distance and time of day.  Call, text or email for more information:  show contact info You'll feel completely taken care of and your knots and stress will be minimized.

Credit cards are accepted with proper identification.  Thirty-minute sessions are given only for regular clients on a case-by-case basis, only for pain-related circumstances, and the cost is $50.Outcall is not available.Enjoy your choice of Swedish, Deep Tissue, and Feathering massages, or a combination of all three -- as well as detailed and focused work on tight, overworked muscles.  Male and Female clients are welcome. Enjoy my very relaxing, private, in-home studio.  Shower available (No -- this is not a shower massage).  A large outdoor hot tub is also available in private surroundings for your personal use, prior to your session, at no extra charge. Draping is required for all clients according to the law of the State of Tennessee.  Non-draping is never an option.

column11: Licensed female massage therapist available, with fifteen years experience. 60 minutes: $80.00/90 minutes: $120.00.   Sessions are scheduled 9:00 a.m. through 7:00 p.m., seven days a week. Credit cards are accepted with proper identification.  Thirty-minute sessions are given only for regular clients on a case-by-case basis, only for pain-related circumstances, and the cost is $50.Outcall is not available.Enjoy your choice of Swedish, Deep Tissue, and Feathering massages, or a combination of all three -- as well as detailed and focused work on tight, overworked muscles.  Male and Female clients are welcome. Enjoy my very relaxing, private, in-home studio.  Shower available (No -- this is not a shower massage).  A large outdoor hot tub is also available in private surroundings for your personal use, prior to your session, at no extra charge. Draping is required for all clients according to the law of the State of Tennessee.  Non-draping is never an option.
